### List all employees

GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees
Accept: application/json

### Find employee by id

GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/1
Accept: application/json

### List addresses for employee

GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/1/addresses
Accept: application/json

### Create employee

POST http://localhost:8080/api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe"
}

### Create address

POST http://localhost:8080/api/employees/1/addresses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "city": "Budapest"
}

### Update

PUT http://localhost:8080/api/employees/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jack Doe"
}

### Delete

DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/employees/1

### Count
GET http://localhost:8080/api/count

### Schedule
POST http://localhost:8080/api/schedule